Package nbt.tag

Class ByteTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • nbt.tag.Tag<java.lang.Byte>
      • nbt.tag.ByteTag
  • public class ByteTag
extends Tag<java.lang.Byte>
    A tag that is designed to hold a single byte and a name that may be associated with it. It follows the specification laid out by the ByteArrayTag in the NBT format.
    Author:
    Killerkoen
